POST http://localhost:3001/api/artisans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Artisan",
  "email": "test@artisanai.in",
  "phone": "+918590955502",
  "whatsappNumber": "+918590955502",
  "craftType": "Pottery",
  "region": "Karnataka",
  "bio": "Traditional pottery maker testing the WhatsApp AI system",
  "language": "english",
  "status": "verified"
}

### Get All Artisans
GET http://localhost:3001/api/artisans

### Get Artisan by Phone
GET http://localhost:3001/api/artisans?phone=+918590955502

### Test Webhook Verification (GET)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/whatsapp/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=artisan_ai_webhook_secret_2026&hub.challenge=test_challenge

### Simulate WhatsApp Message (POST) - For local testing without Twilio
POST http://localhost:3001/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Twilio-Signature: test_signature_for_local_testing

{
  "From": "whatsapp:+918590955502",
  "To": "whatsapp:+14155238886",
  "Body": "Test message",
  "NumMedia": "0",
  "MessageSid": "SM1234567890"
}
